{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Shadowheart avatar finds a hint of Dark Justiciar presence and wonders how her hidden dream.",
    "how_to_trigger": "1. Play avatar Shadowheart2. SetGlobalOsirisFlag ORI_Shadowheart_Event_DarkJusticiarHint in console"
  },
  "dialogue": {
    "2": {
      "id": "2",
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "text": "*You know in your heart that the distant edifice you spied were dedicated to Lady Shar. Only Dark Justiciars could have the strength to built such a grand stronghold.*",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [
        "ORI_Shadowheart_State_AtTempleVista"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "5",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "7": {
          "id": "7",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "*No matter how much of your memory was surrendered to the Nightsinger, you cannot forget about her legendary Justiciars. Her most loyal servants and finest warriors.*",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "5",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "13": {
              "id": "13",
              "speaker": "Narrator",
              "text": "*Once, Lady Shar could lay claim to whole armies of Dark Justiciars... until a mysterious calamity, long in the past, broke their seat of power and bled their ranks away to nothing.*",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "5",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "12": {
                  "id": "12",
                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                  "text": "*Your own Mother Superior revived the tradition, and created new Justiciars. How you longed to become one of them... yet she always denied you.*",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [
                    "ORI_Shadowheart_Knows_BecomeJusticiar"
                  ],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "5",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "1": {
                      "id": "1",
                      "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                      "text": "Something must have caused the Dark Justiciars to vanish as they did. You owe it to Lady Shar to discover what happened to her servants.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "5",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "15": {
                          "id": "15",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*Perhaps you may find a way to prove yourself as well - even join the ranks of the Dark Justiciars.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "5",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "9": {
                      "id": "9",
                      "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                      "text": "The Dark Justiciars' true seat of power must be somewhere nearby. You should find it, and realise your dream at last.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "5",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "0": {
                          "id": "0",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*If you could prove yourself worthy to Lady Shar in a place where her very power caresses the land, then even the Mother Superior could not deny you.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "5": {
                              "id": "5",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*You must press forward, and see what is revealed to you.*",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "14": {
                                  "id": "14",
                                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                                  "text": "*Where the Dark Justiciars of old once walked, perhaps a new one might emerge*",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "3": {
                      "id": "3",
                      "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                      "text": "Perhaps the Mother Superior has her reasons. Perhaps you are not ready.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "5",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "11": {
                          "id": "11",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*Or perhaps the Mother Superior's reasons are a misguided interpretation of Lady Shar's will. The Mother Superior is but a mortal, after all...*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "5",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "4": {
      "id": "4",
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "text": "*You cannot ignore it any longer - there are signs that Dark Justiciars were once a presence in this region.*",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "7",
